_sText:
This map was made by Marco for the use of the volleyball competetion held but is now offered to the public for dl so they can enjoy the map as well.

The map is really designed for 2v2 but can be played with any numbers really. The ball has a very unique texture :) which adds to the fun the net is at good height for both smashing and blocking the gravity is set to 600 and the ball is at good weight. Enjoy!
